import {Component} from "react";
import React, { useState } from "react";

import {
  Row,
  Col,
  Card,
  Form,
  InputGroup,
  FormControl,
  Button,
} from "react-bootstrap";


class RegisterComponent extends Component {
    render() {
        return(
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
            <Col xs={5}>
              <Card className={"border border-dark bg-dark text-white"}>
                <Card.Header>
                   Register
                </Card.Header>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Form.Row>
                    <Form.Group as={Col}>
                      <InputGroup>
                        <InputGroup.Prepend>
                          <InputGroup.Text>
                        

                          </InputGroup.Text>
                        </InputGroup.Prepend>
                        <FormControl
                          autoComplete="off"
                          type="text"
                          name="name"
                          
                          
                          className={"bg-dark text-white"}
                          placeholder="Enter Name"
                        />
                      </InputGroup>
                    </Form.Group>
                  </Form.Row>
                  </Card.Body>
                  </Card>
                  </Col>
                  </Row>
        )
    }
}

export default RegisterComponent
